《'''痞子猫'''》（{{lang-en|Bad Cat}}）是一部[[土耳其|土耳其]]的动画、喜剧、电影<ref>{{cite news|last1=Brzeski|first1=Patrick|title=Filmart: Raunchy Animated Film 'Bad Cat' Sells to China, Middle East (Exclusive)|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/bad-cat-sells-china-middle-874981|accessdate=13 March 2016|publisher=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2016-03-13|archive-date=2016-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314094914/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/bad-cat-sells-china-middle-874981|dead-url=no}}</ref>

